{"tid":1507752,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人是新黑5類, 是高危人種, 你地小心, 不要番中国","createTime":"2019-08-26T09:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T06:59:16.000Z","uid":76310,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b6be99ae4e9e560d05bb2587a490e4bf3a3dddd1","tid":1507752,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:39:24.000Z","msg":"香港人是新黑5類, 是高危人種, 你地小心, 不要番中国<br />\n香港人在中国人眼中, 在中央眼中, 在中共眼中就是攪事, 勾結外國勢力<br />\n回中国是十分高危<br />\n<br />\n中国人極端民族主義上腦, 不會有什麼理性可言<br />\n我知道你說什麼, 你說我是中立的, 支持政府的, 不會有事<br />\n那你完全錯了, 首先中国人不會和你講什麼道理, 他們都是生番<br />\n而且, 中国經濟轉差, 見你是香港人, 就會老屈, 想辦法勒索<br />\n<br />\n所以, 不要番中国就是安全<br />\n香港是新黑5類, 是高危人種, 被視為不愛国愛黨, 勾結外國勢力的族群, 中国人是生番, 不講任何道理, 他們什麼都做得出"},{"pid":"ae74efbba7610d2cbe74d42b6b635e1de7bb7529","tid":1507752,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:39:58.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY%2FMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=9a2cb04e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"96b13b680111db2ac53c268ac2b5b8458b7718e5","tid":1507752,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:42:05.000Z","msg":"求翻譯<br />\n利申閱讀理解5**"},{"pid":"562d03709447a3770b9f1b931808a8eee58e6dd8","tid":1507752,"uid":94828,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"96b13b680111db2ac53c268ac2b5b8458b7718e5","tid":1507752,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:42:05.000Z","msg":"求翻譯<br />\n利申閱讀理解5**"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:47:32.000Z","msg":"你中史u?"},{"pid":"b46fe9a575ff04b0e91db2e03307c08db1a47b15","tid":1507752,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0